    Internal plugin interface for pending change UI.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      Map<IEntityType,Class<DiffDisplay>> DiffDisplayTypes
      Returns a map of diff display types by entity type. Out of the box implementation returns a KeyableBeanDiffDisplay for all entity types. The keys in the map should all be entity types (e.g. Address, Policy etc.) The values should be Gosu classes which implement the DiffDisplay interface.
      Tree<IEntityType> DisplayTree
      Configuration for converting the entity graph into a tree structure to display in the UI
      Set<IPropertyInfo> EntityPropertiesToIgnoreForComparison
      Set of properties in the entity graph to ignore when determining if the policies under comparison actually have differences.
      Map<IEntityType,Class<EntityMatcher<KeyableBean>>> MatcherTypes
      Returns a map of matcher types by entity type. Out of the box implementation matches only on LinkID. The keys in the map should all be entity types (e.g. Address, ABContact etc.) The values should be Gosu classes which implement the EntityMatcher interface.
